---
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/Base';
import Link from '@/components/Link';
import Heading from '@/components/Heading';
import Paragraph from '@/components/Paragraph';
import SocialList from '@/components/SocialList';

const meta = {
	title: 'About',
	description: "Chris Vaillancourt's background",
};
---

<PageLayout meta={meta}>
	<article>
		<Heading level="1">About</Heading>
		<section>
			<Heading level="2">What I do</Heading>
			<Paragraph>
				I'm a full stack software engineer, proficient in
				<Link primary href="https://www.typescriptlang.org/">TypeScript</Link>
				and
				<Link primary href="https://www.python.org/">Python</Link>. I love
				building interactive data-driven applications, backend services, and
				developer tools.
			</Paragraph>
			<Paragraph>
				I primarily build user interfaces with
				<Link primary href="https://vuejs.org/">Vue.js</Link>
				but am experienced in other frameworks including
				<Link primary href="https://react.dev/">React</Link>,
				<Link primary href="https://www.solidjs.com/">Solid.js</Link>,
				<Link primary href="https://svelte.dev/">Svelte</Link>,
				<Link primary href="https://astro.build/">Astro</Link>, and vanilla
				JavaScript.
			</Paragraph>
			<Paragraph>
				I currently develop back end API's in Python using
				<Link primary href="https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/">FastAPI</Link>
				and in Node.js using
				<Link primary href="https://www.fastify.io/">Fastify</Link>.
			</Paragraph>
		</section>
		<section>
			<Heading level="2">What I've Done</Heading>
			<Paragraph>
				I started my career as a cartographer at
				<Link href="https://www.esri.com/">Esri</Link>, building maps for
				journalists and large media outlets. During that time, I learned to use
				HTML, CSS, and JavaScript to create custom visualizations for a variety
				of media clients.
			</Paragraph>
			<Paragraph>
				After going deep on data visualization, I joined Denovium as a user
				interface software engineer. During this time I helped develop the
				Denovium Gateway, a web application that used AI models to create and
				explore entire genomes. The platform we developed ultimately led to our
				<span class="inline-flex">
					<Link
						primary
						href="https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/absci-announces-acquisition-of-deep-learning-company-denovium-301206116.html"
					>
						acquisition by Absci
					</Link>.
				</span>
			</Paragraph>
			<Paragraph>
				Today, I work at the intersection of AI and software engineering at
				Absci. As part of the AI engineering team, I'm focused on scaling our AI
				platform and building AI powered tools that expedite workflows and
				reveal novel insights.
			</Paragraph>
		</section>
		<section>
			<Heading level="2">What I'm interested in</Heading>
			<Paragraph>
				I'm passionate about clean code and empathetic collaboration. I thrive
				in cross-functional environments and have extensive experience
				partnering with technical and non-technical colleagues to deliver full
				stack solutions at scale.
			</Paragraph>
		</section>
		<footer class="flex justify-center">
			<SocialList />
		</footer>
	</article>
</PageLayout>
